{"lemma":"دَرَكِ","slug":"دَرَكِ","root":"د.ر.ك","root_slug":"د-ر-ك","root_link":"/words/roots/د-ر-ك","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"دَرَك","root":"درك","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n12457","n12464","n12465"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AF%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%83%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"gendarmerie"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"stairs, staircase going down","tags":["obsolete"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"path one takes to reach a goal"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"reaching of a goal"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a piece rope attached to the side of a bigger rope","tags":["obsolete"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"depth, (literal) rock-bottom","examples":[{"text":"إِنَّ ٱلْمُنَـٰفِقِينَ فِى ٱلدَّرْكِ ٱلْأَسْفَلِ مِنَ ٱلنَّارِ وَلَن تَجِدَ لَهُمْ نَصِيرًا","english":"Surely the hypocrites will be in the lowest depths of the Fire—and you will never find for them any helper."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to last, to continue (of periodic rains)"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root د ر ك (d r k). Cognate with Hebrew דרך (dereḵ) and Aramaic דְּרַךְ (dəraḵ, “to tread”)."},"ipa":["/da.rak/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n12457","headword_ar":"دَرَكَ","root":"drk","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", from which should be derived"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daraAki","text_ar":"دَرَاكِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dar~aAkN","text_ar":"دَرَّاكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", is unused, though its noun"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"drk","text_ar":"درك"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darokN","text_ar":"دَرْكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darakN","text_ar":"دَرَكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which latter (the more common of the two) see below,] is used. (IB.) ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daraka","text_ar":"دَرَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in Golius's Lex. is evidently a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAraka","text_ar":"دَارَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n12464","headword_ar":"دَرْكٌ","root":"drk","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next paragraph, in eight places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n12465","headword_ar":"دَرَكٌ","root":"drk","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attaining, reaching,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overtaking;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laHaAqN","text_ar":"لَحَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, TA; [in the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"All~iHAqu","text_ar":"اللِّحاقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"All~aHaAqu","text_ar":"اللَّحَاقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":";]) [properly an inf. n. of the unused verb"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daraka","text_ar":"دَرَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(q. v.), but, having no used verb, said to be] a noun from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA_idoraAku","text_ar":"الاـِدْرَاكُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[with which it is syn.], (TA,) or a noun from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adorakotu Al$~aYo'a","text_ar":"اَدْرَكْتُ الشَّىْءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darokN","text_ar":"دَرْكٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": and hence"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DamaAnN","text_ar":"ضَمَانٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~araki","text_ar":"الدَّرَكِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which see in what follows]. (Msb.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA taxaAfu darakFA","text_ar":"لَا تَخَافُ دَرَكًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [xx. 80.], means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thou shalt not fear"},{"kind":"text","text":"Pharaoh's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overtaking"},{"kind":"text","text":"thee. (TA.) One says also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~arydapi","text_ar":"الطَّريدَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"farasN daroku","text_ar":"فَرَسٌ دَرْكُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A horse that overtakes what is hunted;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like as they said"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"farasN qayodu AlA^awaAbidi","text_ar":"فَرَسٌ قَيْدُ الاَوَابِدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-  ―         -b3-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attainment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"acquisition, of an object of want:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"seeking the attainment"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"acquisition thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bak~iro fafiyhi","text_ar":"بَكِّرْ فَفِيهِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darakN","text_ar":"دَرَكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Be thou early; for therein is attainment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darokN","text_ar":"دَرْكٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same. (Lth, TA.) [Hence, perhaps,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomu Ald~arika","text_ar":"يَوْمُ الدَّرِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": this was [a day of contest] between El-Ows and El-Khazraj: (K:) thought to be so by IDrd. (TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tabiEapN","text_ar":"تَبِعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A consequence;"},{"kind":"text","text":"generally meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an evil consequence:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and perhaps it also means here"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a claim which one seeks to obtain for an injury"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darokN","text_ar":"دَرْكٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA laHiqaka mino","text_ar":"مَا لَحِقَكَ مِنْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darakK faEalaY~i xalaASuhu","text_ar":"دَرَكٍ فَعَلَىِّ خَلَاصُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mn darokK","text_ar":"من دَرْكٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Whatever evil consequence ensue to thee, on me be the compensation thereof"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: in the A,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mA A^adorakahu","text_ar":"ما اَدْرَكَهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mn darakK fElY~ xlASh","text_ar":"من دَرَكٍ فعلىّ خلاصه"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA yaloHaquhu mino tabiEapK","text_ar":"مَا يَلْحَقُهُ مِنْ تَبِعَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Whatever evil consequence ensue to it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; relating to a thing sold]. (TA.) And hence"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DamaAnu Ald~araki","text_ar":"ضَمَانُ الدَّرَكِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the case of a claim for indemnification for a fault of a defect or an imperfection in a thing sold [meaning either"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Responsibility,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"indemnification,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DamaAnN","text_ar":"ضَمَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for evil consequence"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA in the present art:) or this means ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"indemnification for evil consequence in a sale;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e., virtually,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the returning of the price to the purchaser on the occasion of requirement by the thing sold:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the vulgar say incorrectly ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DamaAn darak","text_ar":"ضَمَان دَرَك"},{"kind":"text","text":", and still more incorrectly]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DumaAn darak","text_ar":"ضُمَان دَرَك"},{"kind":"text","text":"[generally meaning thereby I sell this, or I purchase this, on the condition of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"responsibility,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"indemnification, for any fault"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"defect"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"imperfection"},{"kind":"text","text":"that may be found in it]: (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dmn","text_ar":"ضمن"},{"kind":"text","text":":) [and in this manner"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DamaAnu Ald~araki","text_ar":"ضَمَانُ الدَّرَكِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"may be correctly rendered; for]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darakN","text_ar":"دَرَكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a fault"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a defect"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an imperfection"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in a thing sold]; for instance, in a slave that is sold. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ehd","text_ar":"عهد"},{"kind":"text","text":".) [In the KT,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~araku","text_ar":"الدَّرَكُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also explained as signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The purchaser's taking from the seller a pledge for the price that he has given him, in fear that the thing sold may require it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but this seems to be an explanation of the case in which the word is used; not of the word itself.]       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A rope,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a piece of rope,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is tied upon the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lower"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extremity of the main rope"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a well, to the cross pieces of wood of the bucket,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so as to be that which is next the water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in order that the main rope may not rot"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the drawing of water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a doubled rope that is tied to the cross pieces of wood of the bucket, and then to the main wellrope:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darokN","text_ar":"دَرْكٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same. (K. [But only"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darakN","text_ar":"دَرَكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is authorized by the TA in this sense.]) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"karabN","text_ar":"كَرَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  Also, and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darokN","text_ar":"دَرْكٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bottom,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lowest depth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, T, S, M, K,) of a thing, (T, M, K,) as of the sea and the like, (T,) or of anything deep, as a well and the like: (Sh:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adoraAkN","text_ar":"اَدْرَاكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) a pl. of both, of a form frequent and analogous with respect to the former, but extr. with respect to the latter; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darakaAtN","text_ar":"دَرَكَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A stage"},{"kind":"text","text":"of Hell: (IAar:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a stage downwards:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stages downwards;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darakaAtN","text_ar":"دَرَكَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (B:) opposed to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darajN","text_ar":"دَرَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA, B) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darajaAtN","text_ar":"دَرَجَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (B,) which are upwards: wherefore, (MA, B,) the abodes of Hell, or the stages thereof, are termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darakaAtN","text_ar":"دَرَكَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (AO, S, MA, K, B;) [Golius and Freytag give"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darakapN","text_ar":"دَرَكَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as its sing.; the former as from the S, and the latter as from the K, in neither of which it is found;] and those of Paradise,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darajaAtN","text_ar":"دَرَجَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, MA, B.) It is said in the Kur [iv. 144],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~a A@lomunaAfiqiyna fiYA@ld~araki","text_ar":"اـِنَّ ا@لْمُنَافِقِينَ فِىا@لدَّرَكِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@loA^asofali mina A@ln~aAri","text_ar":"ا@لْاَسْفَلِ مِنَ ا@لنَّارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily the hypocrites"},{"kind":"text","text":"shall be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the lowest stage of the fire"},{"kind":"text","text":"of Hell]: here the Koofees, except two, read ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fY Ald~aroki","text_ar":"فى الدَّرْكِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-  [Golius gives another signification, “"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Pars terræ,"},{"kind":"text","text":"” as on the authority of the S and K, in neither of which it is found.]"}],"source_refs":["TA","K","S","M","Az","Sh","T","IAar","MA","B"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}